\newlabel{fig:sim-recovery}{{5}{13}{Univariate simulated HMM benchmark. The observed series has clear stress-state bursts, and all three samplers recover plausible average state occupancy, but chain diagnostics remain poor. This indicates that reasonable-looking state probabilities can coexist with unreliable posterior sampling}{figure.5}{}}
